NOTICE FOR THE BUNDLE:
- Individual photographs from Wikimedia Commons retain their original licenses
  (mostly CC-BY-SA-4.0). Complete attribution is visible in each <figcaption>
  of the live site (https://sociedad.opitacode.com) and in VISUAL-HONESTY.md.
- 2 AI-generated portraits are explicitly declared as "Retrato AI — no
  fotográfico documental" in the live site.
- 7 typographic SVG markers are used as honest placeholders until real
  photography with explicit consent becomes available.

NOTICE FOR SOURCE CODE:
- The source code of this bundle (Astro project) is not publicly versioned in
  this repository. The bundle is the compiled output of an Astro 5 + React 19
  + Tailwind 3.4 + Pixi.js 8.6 + D3 7.9 project. The source code lives in a
  private repository maintained by the operator. If you want to adapt the
  source, please contact the operator via WhatsApp (+57 312 612 6085) or email
  replicas@opitacode.com.

